{
  "stem": "17337.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 301.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because you know, I could still sneak out from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, there was a time you could sneak out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said, you have nothing left to lose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Go.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It cannot be worse than here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even he didn't know either.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he knew-- he heard about Schindler.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he didn't know what it is then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's how I got from Plaszow to Schindler.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the following days, they send us, because Schindler had his factories in Krakow, not in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that-- we were not the only group, 15 people that came, you know, but-- but maybe 200 people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we were one of the groups.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And what we-- they used to manufacture their pots and pan, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But our job was to build ammunition factory because you see, to-- to have a factory in pots and pans, that's not for-- for-- for-- for war, you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He couldn't-- he couldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he started to build a-- a factory from ammunition.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember he came in the first day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was a brick yard, a big place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so much loaded on it, you know, and we had to clean that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In one day, they have to clean that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And after that one day, I said to myself, I should better stay in Plaszow than to come here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But after that, it started to get better.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We started to-- to build that factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And in between, we used to go to there and make-- help out in pots and pans too, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we used to get the soup, extra soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
